'''Trade Barons''' were officials in the [[Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Federation]] whom were underneath the [[Viceroy of the Trade Federation/Legends|Trade Viceroy]].

[[Lott Dod/Legends|Lott Dod's]] two aides in the [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Galactic Senate]], the diplomat [[Lufa Danak/Legends|Lufa Danak]] and the financial officer [[Mik Regrap]], were Trade Barons.

Another Trade Baron was [[Uunos Gooru]], whose biography was written by [[Viff Almay]].

